when : BOX 1. I introuduce valid email account, system recognizes a valid mail has been place at the box , with a green tick at the BOX
---------------------------------------------------------------------
when: I get 5 BOXES filled a confirmation message is displayed  (information has been succesfully introduced and e-mail has been sent the email provide pleas confrim link reieved)
Then: I go to my email and get to the LINK where it is said e-mail confirmation. 
Then I click it and back to www.venturedestination.com I am now LOG IN

2. Scenario: Wrong or not valid e.mail address (when confirmation link can not be sent by system to e/mail provided)
